{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ceiling","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/ceiling","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath 참고 문서</a></b>: <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 요소</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 함수</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 축</a>\n</div><p></p>\n<p><br>\n <code>ceiling</code> 함수는 10진수를 평가하고 10진수보다 작지 않은 가장 작은 정수를 반환합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.ac.b8.eb.b2.95","title":"문법","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">ceiling(<i>number</i> )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.9d.b8.ec.88.98","title":"인수","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect2\">\n  <code>\n  <i>\n   number</i>\n  </code></dt>\n <dd>\n  평가할 수.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.b0.98.ed.99.98","title":"반환","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>\n <i>\n  number</i>\n </code>보다 작지 않은 가장 작은 정수.</p>\n<p>예를 들어,</p>\n<p><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ceiling (\n <i>\n  5.2</i>\n )</code> = <var>6</var></p>\n<p><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ceiling (\n <i>\n  -5.2</i>\n )</code> = <var>-5</var></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a0.95.ec.9d.98","title":"정의","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-ceiling\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.4</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_.ec.a7.80.ec.9b.90","title":"Gecko 지원","isH3":true,"content":"<p>지원함.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"ceiling 함수는 10진수를 평가하고 10진수보다 작지 않은 가장 작은 정수를 반환합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ceiling","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ceiling","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":